        hkask:HkaskError-NotFound, hkask:HkaskError-RateLimitExceeded,
        hkask:HkaskError-RateLimitExceededWithRetry, hkask:HkaskError-CapabilityDenied,
        hkask:HkaskError-InvalidToken, hkask:HkaskError-PermissionDenied,
